1
00:00:46,120 --> 00:00:47,250
Who exactly are you?

2
00:00:47,920 --> 00:00:48,600
Aran.

3
00:00:49,440 --> 00:00:50,360
I am Ayin.

4
00:00:50,760 --> 00:00:51,720
What's wrong?

5
00:00:51,880 --> 00:00:52,680
Speak.

6
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:54,280
Who are you really?

7
00:00:54,960 --> 00:00:56,360
Why did you approach me?

8
00:00:56,360 --> 00:00:57,360
What do you want?

9
00:01:03,160 --> 00:01:04,560
I adore you.

10
00:01:05,319 --> 00:01:06,960
I want to be with you forever.

11
00:01:12,840 --> 00:01:13,640
You...

12
00:01:14,720 --> 00:01:16,080
You are a Demon.

13
00:01:18,280 --> 00:01:19,080
Aran.

14
00:01:20,280 --> 00:01:21,560
Be my Queen.

15
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:26,400
You are the Demon Lord.

16
00:01:26,760 --> 00:01:27,560
Aran.

17
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:29,560
Marry me.

18
00:01:30,960 --> 00:01:31,880
In your dreams.

19
00:01:33,080 --> 00:01:34,880
Immortals and Demons are on different paths.

20
00:01:34,880 --> 00:01:36,960
We don't belong to the same world.

21
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:38,560
Don't be delusional.

22
00:01:41,360 --> 00:01:42,420
Those villages...

23
00:01:43,440 --> 00:01:44,960
Did you do that to those villages?

24
00:01:44,960 --> 00:01:46,640
Did you kill those people?

25
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:47,560
No.

26
00:01:47,759 --> 00:01:48,560
Aran.

27
00:01:49,560 --> 00:01:51,560
You care about the common people.

28
00:01:51,960 --> 00:01:54,160
How could I harm them?

29
00:01:55,160 --> 00:01:55,960
Aran.

30
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:57,840
Marry me.

31
00:01:58,680 --> 00:02:00,640
Let us protect the world together.

32
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:02,140
What do you say?

33
00:02:05,160 --> 00:02:06,520
Where are those people?

34
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:09,360
They have been settled properly.

35
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,419
Don't worry, Aran.

36
00:02:13,880 --> 00:02:16,240
On the day of our grand wedding,

37
00:02:16,760 --> 00:02:18,880
I will make sure the whole world

38
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:20,960
comes to congratulate us.

39
00:02:25,480 --> 00:02:28,160
Whatever you want then,

40
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:30,160
I will give it to you.

41
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:34,500
You've lost your mind.

42
00:03:02,440 --> 00:03:03,160
Open it.

43
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:05,160
The barrier you set yourself,

44
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:06,620
even you can't open it.

45
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:08,040
How could I open it?

46
00:03:08,160 --> 00:03:08,960
You...

47
00:03:11,320 --> 00:03:12,980
Don't think this will hold me.

48
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:25,360
Let me go.

49
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:28,600
Are you all right?

50
00:03:28,600 --> 00:03:29,530
Senior Brother.

51
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:32,360
I'm fine.

52
00:03:33,079 --> 00:03:34,240
Why are you here?

53
00:03:34,720 --> 00:03:36,360
To take you back, of course.

54
00:03:36,720 --> 00:03:38,360
To be my Heavenly Queen.

55
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:43,160
I will settle today's score with you

56
00:03:43,160 --> 00:03:44,960
another day.

57
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:46,920
Let's go.

58
00:04:09,760 --> 00:04:10,560
Ayin.

59
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:12,840
Have you gone mad?

60
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:16,760
Aran.

61
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:20,360
I just want you to be my wife.

62
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:22,360
Lunatic.

63
00:04:23,080 --> 00:04:26,410
Do you not know Immortals and Demons are on different paths?

64
00:04:26,960 --> 00:04:28,680
Senior Brother will soon find out I'm missing.

65
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:30,410
He will definitely come for me.

66
00:04:30,760 --> 00:04:32,820
And I will only marry Senior Brother.

67
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:34,360
I said I would marry you.

68
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:36,080
And I will.

69
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:39,720
Aran.

70
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:41,320
It's only been a few days.

71
00:04:41,640 --> 00:04:44,159
and you're about to marry your Senior Brother?

72
00:04:44,159 --> 00:04:45,159
Is it...

73
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:47,980
just because he is the Heavenly Emperor?

74
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:50,159
Don't touch me.

75
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:52,640
Since Aran

76
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:55,640
does not want to be the Queen of our Demon Tribe,

77
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:57,760
then I will kill the Heavenly Emperor,

78
00:04:57,760 --> 00:04:59,159
unify the Three Realms,

79
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:01,320
and let you continue to be

80
00:05:01,520 --> 00:05:02,720
the Heavenly Queen.

81
00:05:03,640 --> 00:05:04,680
Lunatic.

82
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:12,040
Where am I?

83
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:14,840
Does it feel familiar?

84
00:05:16,760 --> 00:05:17,620
Very familiar?

85
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:21,800
I built this especially for you in the Demon Realm.

86
00:05:22,760 --> 00:05:26,090
It's a little different from our cottage in the Human Realm,

87
00:05:27,480 --> 00:05:28,960
but don't worry, Aran.

88
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:31,360
I promise to turn the Demon Realm

89
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:33,920
into a colorful new world.

90
00:05:35,760 --> 00:05:37,280
I won't allow

91
00:05:37,280 --> 00:05:39,320
you to do anything to harm the innocent.

92
00:05:39,320 --> 00:05:40,040
Okay.

93
00:05:41,440 --> 00:05:42,770
Whatever you say, Aran.

94
00:05:49,960 --> 00:05:51,120
Later,

95
00:05:51,640 --> 00:05:53,570
I'll come back to keep you company.

96
00:06:04,640 --> 00:06:05,440
My Lord.

97
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:06,960
Did you find it?

98
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:08,360
My Lord,

99
00:06:08,880 --> 00:06:09,760
I found out that

100
00:06:09,760 --> 00:06:11,880
the Spirit Pearl passed down by the Dragon Clan

101
00:06:11,880 --> 00:06:13,680
is the key to obtaining the Seven-Colored Stone.

102
00:06:13,680 --> 00:06:14,640
The Dragon Clan.

103
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:18,640
No wonder I traveled the Human Realm for so long

104
00:06:18,760 --> 00:06:19,960
and never found it.

105
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:25,160
Speak your mind.

106
00:06:25,640 --> 00:06:27,360
I'm in a good mood today.

107
00:06:27,840 --> 00:06:28,900
I wanted to say that

108
00:06:29,880 --> 00:06:32,440
the Dragon Clan and the Heavenly Clan have been allies for generations.

109
00:06:32,440 --> 00:06:33,920
With the Heavenly Queen now in the Demon Realm,

110
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:35,980
if we try to take the Spirit Pearl now,

111
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:38,520
it might force the Dragon and Heavenly Clans to join forces

112
00:06:38,520 --> 00:06:39,920
against us.

113
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:42,640
And your injuries haven't fully healed.

114
00:06:42,640 --> 00:06:43,560
I am worried...

115
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:44,960
My injuries are fine.

116
00:06:45,440 --> 00:06:47,360
Regarding my wedding tomorrow,

117
00:06:47,520 --> 00:06:49,520
handle the arrangements yourself.

118
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:50,330
Yes, My Lord.

119
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:11,440
The Love-Locking Curse.

120
00:07:12,960 --> 00:07:14,560
The so-called righteous Heavenly Clan.

121
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:16,560
Nothing but despicable hypocrites.

122
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:18,490
They actually cast a curse on Aran.

123
00:07:33,400 --> 00:07:34,280
Who?

124
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:36,960
Who broke the Love-Locking Curse?

125
00:07:43,520 --> 00:07:44,050
It was...

126
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:44,770
It was...

127
00:07:46,280 --> 00:07:49,159
Don't even think about escaping the Demon Realm.

128
00:07:50,440 --> 00:07:51,960
Why did you seal my powers?

129
00:07:52,159 --> 00:07:53,560
To keep you from running away, of course.

130
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:53,960
You...

131
00:07:55,640 --> 00:07:57,360
You're certainly direct.

132
00:07:58,560 --> 00:07:59,360
Aran.

133
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:01,960
My feelings for you are real.

134
00:08:02,440 --> 00:08:03,720
I've never lied to you.

135
00:08:05,840 --> 00:08:06,560
Aran.

136
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:09,440
We spent so much time together in the Human Realm.

137
00:08:09,440 --> 00:08:12,360
Didn't you feel anything for Ayin?

138
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:14,960
Not even a little bit?

139
00:08:15,760 --> 00:08:16,560
Feelings?

140
00:08:51,560 --> 00:08:52,360
Aran.

141
00:09:12,240 --> 00:09:13,320
Turn around.

142
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:14,480
Don't look.

143
00:09:14,560 --> 00:09:15,120
Oh.

144
00:09:24,560 --> 00:09:26,440
I'll go get some food.

145
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:46,880
Earlier...

146
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:50,440
Oh.

147
00:09:52,240 --> 00:09:54,170
The fruit I picked is really sweet.

148
00:09:54,280 --> 00:09:55,120
Taste it.

149
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:00,320
How is it?

150
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:01,160
Is it sweet?

151
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:09,410
I think it's sweet, too.

152
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:14,720
Is this what love feels like?

153
00:10:14,920 --> 00:10:15,720
No.

154
00:10:16,160 --> 00:10:17,720
I've known for as long as I can remember

155
00:10:17,720 --> 00:10:19,480
that Senior Brother is my destiny.

156
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:21,360
I must protect the world with him.

157
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:24,170
I couldn't possibly fall for another man.

158
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:27,320
No.

159
00:10:32,560 --> 00:10:33,690
I don't believe you.

160
00:10:34,880 --> 00:10:36,120
You can lie,

161
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:38,640
but your eyes and your heart

162
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:40,360
cannot.

163
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:46,010
I can only marry my Senior Brother.

164
00:10:46,760 --> 00:10:48,220
From the moment I was born,

165
00:10:48,560 --> 00:10:50,840
my destiny with him was sealed.

166
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:53,120
Aran,

167
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:56,520
no destiny is sealed at birth.

168
00:10:56,680 --> 00:10:57,760
He is lying to you.

169
00:11:02,160 --> 00:11:04,880
Don't try to drive a wedge between Senior Brother and me.

170
00:11:04,880 --> 00:11:06,560
He would never lie to me.

171
00:11:10,480 --> 00:11:11,480
It doesn't matter.

172
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:13,540
If you don't want to admit to the past,

173
00:11:13,640 --> 00:11:14,840
that's fine.

174
00:11:15,680 --> 00:11:16,880
But from now on,

175
00:11:17,520 --> 00:11:19,650
you will remember your true feelings.

176
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:23,300
Without the Love-Locking Spell,

177
00:11:23,560 --> 00:11:27,680
I'd like to see how that Heavenly Emperor controls you now.

178
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:30,520
I'm tired.

179
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:32,360
I need to rest.

180
00:11:33,160 --> 00:11:34,080
Please leave.

181
00:11:34,560 --> 00:11:35,160
All right.

182
00:11:35,560 --> 00:11:36,760
Rest well.

183
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:38,680
After tomorrow,

184
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:41,320
we will never be apart again.

185
00:11:51,160 --> 00:11:53,960
Goddess Xingran's Love-Locking Spell is broken.

186
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:55,290
What is destined to come

187
00:11:55,600 --> 00:11:57,360
will come eventually.

188
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:07,200
A Love Tribulation.

189
00:12:07,600 --> 00:12:08,560
How is she?

190
00:12:09,040 --> 00:12:10,640
Why hasn't Aran woken up yet?

191
00:12:11,160 --> 00:12:14,120
Goddess Xingran was struck by spiritual power from two realms.

192
00:12:14,120 --> 00:12:15,520
Her internal organs are shattered,

193
00:12:15,520 --> 00:12:16,960
and her spiritual roots are damaged.

194
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:18,960
She needs daily spiritual healing

195
00:12:18,960 --> 00:12:19,960
to recover.

196
00:12:20,440 --> 00:12:21,240
Okay.

197
00:12:22,040 --> 00:12:24,960
Then I will transfer spiritual power to her every day

198
00:12:24,960 --> 00:12:26,420
until she is fully healed.

199
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:27,920
Your Majesty,

200
00:12:28,720 --> 00:12:31,640
there is something I don't know if I should mention.

201
00:12:31,960 --> 00:12:33,620
It concerns Aran's injuries.

202
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:34,880
Speak freely.

203
00:12:34,880 --> 00:12:35,880
Do not hide anything.

204
00:12:35,880 --> 00:12:36,720
Her injuries are not critical.

205
00:12:36,720 --> 00:12:37,850
They can be treated.

206
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:39,160
However,

207
00:12:39,720 --> 00:12:40,520
just now,

208
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:44,240
I accidentally discovered an anomaly in her Love Vein.

209
00:12:49,760 --> 00:12:50,890
What does that mean?

210
00:12:52,520 --> 00:12:53,320
Soon,

211
00:12:53,880 --> 00:12:56,320
Goddess Xingran will face a Love Tribulation.

212
00:12:56,320 --> 00:12:59,680
And this tribulation may alter the fate of many,

213
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:01,760
including yours, Your Majesty.

214
00:13:02,560 --> 00:13:04,360
I fear for your throne...

215
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:06,960
Are you saying

216
00:13:07,960 --> 00:13:09,960
that Aran's husband will not be me,

217
00:13:10,160 --> 00:13:11,240
but someone else?

218
00:13:11,880 --> 00:13:13,160
The variables are too great.

219
00:13:13,160 --> 00:13:15,020
I dare not make wild predictions.

220
00:13:28,160 --> 00:13:29,560
The Love-Locking Spell.

221
00:13:30,560 --> 00:13:32,040
Use the Love-Locking Spell.

222
00:13:32,040 --> 00:13:33,360
Seal Aran's Love Vein

223
00:13:33,960 --> 00:13:36,120
so she cannot fall in love with anyone else.

224
00:13:36,120 --> 00:13:37,850
That is a forbidden technique.

225
00:13:38,320 --> 00:13:39,560
The Ancestral Emperor long ago decreed

226
00:13:39,560 --> 00:13:41,560
that no forbidden techniques are to be used.

227
00:13:41,560 --> 00:13:42,560
Moreover,

228
00:13:42,880 --> 00:13:45,040
given Goddess Xingran's current condition,

229
00:13:45,040 --> 00:13:46,760
she cannot withstand the spell.

230
00:13:46,760 --> 00:13:47,960
Such a forbidden technique...

231
00:13:47,960 --> 00:13:49,480
What would you have me do?

232
00:13:49,840 --> 00:13:52,760
Watch helplessly as she falls for another?

233
00:13:53,760 --> 00:13:55,440
Watch her take

234
00:13:55,440 --> 00:13:57,920
the Phoenix Tribe's hundred thousand elites,

235
00:13:57,920 --> 00:13:58,760
marry someone else,

236
00:13:58,760 --> 00:14:01,160
and become a threat to the Celestial Tribe?

237
00:14:01,760 --> 00:14:03,680
Goddess Xingran was raised to be the Heavenly Empress.

238
00:14:03,680 --> 00:14:04,960
She wouldn't do that.

239
00:14:06,040 --> 00:14:07,960
I'm just being cautious.

240
00:14:09,040 --> 00:14:10,240
After all, I...

241
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:12,280
...love her.

242
00:14:25,560 --> 00:14:28,760
Welcome to my wedding.

243
00:14:29,080 --> 00:14:29,760
Ye Yin.

244
00:14:30,600 --> 00:14:32,260
Hand over the Heavenly Queen.

245
00:14:32,360 --> 00:14:33,880
Here with me,

246
00:14:34,240 --> 00:14:35,560
there is no Heavenly Queen.

247
00:14:35,560 --> 00:14:36,480
There is only

248
00:14:36,960 --> 00:14:38,080
the Queen.

249
00:14:38,360 --> 00:14:39,760
Hand over Ah Ran.

250
00:14:40,680 --> 00:14:43,360
Or I will bathe your Demon Realm in blood.

251
00:14:47,320 --> 00:14:49,080
If you're here for the wedding,

252
00:14:49,760 --> 00:14:51,920
I welcome you.

253
00:14:52,360 --> 00:14:54,160
If you're here to cause trouble,

254
00:14:54,320 --> 00:14:57,680
then let's see if you're capable.

255
00:15:33,040 --> 00:15:33,920
What happened?

256
00:15:34,640 --> 00:15:35,280
Ah Yin?

257
00:15:35,920 --> 00:15:37,050
Let's go take a look.

258
00:15:56,480 --> 00:15:57,480
It really opened.

259
00:16:14,240 --> 00:16:14,920
Ah Ran.

260
00:16:16,520 --> 00:16:18,760
The one who put the Love-Locking Curse on Ah Ran

261
00:16:18,760 --> 00:16:20,690
doesn't deserve to speak her name.

262
00:16:20,840 --> 00:16:22,880
So you broke the Love-Locking Curse.

263
00:16:22,880 --> 00:16:24,160
If it weren't for me,

264
00:16:24,680 --> 00:16:26,010
I wouldn't have guessed

265
00:16:26,440 --> 00:16:29,960
that the Heavenly Emperor who preaches justice

266
00:16:30,680 --> 00:16:32,480
could be so despicable.

267
00:16:32,560 --> 00:16:34,520
Even without the Love-Locking Curse,

268
00:16:34,520 --> 00:16:35,320
Ah Ran...

269
00:16:35,920 --> 00:16:37,120
...she still belongs to me.

270
00:16:37,120 --> 00:16:38,360
In your dreams.

271
00:16:41,320 --> 00:16:43,520
I won't give you that chance.

272
00:16:52,680 --> 00:16:53,840
Stop!

273
00:16:59,640 --> 00:17:00,640
My Queen.

274
00:17:00,640 --> 00:17:02,040
His Lordship gave orders.

275
00:17:02,040 --> 00:17:04,480
This is between him and the Heavenly Emperor.

276
00:17:04,480 --> 00:17:06,480
If you don't want to trigger a war between immortals and demons,

277
00:17:06,480 --> 00:17:08,079
and see corpses everywhere,

278
00:17:08,560 --> 00:17:10,280
please stay by my side.
